The reply of the States Generall of the United Provinces of the Low Countrys, to the letter of the King of Great Brittain United Provinces of the Netherlands. Staten Generaal. Fagel, H.
8, p.
[s.n.], [Hague] : anno 1673.
Signed on p.8: H. Fagel. Place of publication from Wing. Caption title on p.3 reads: To the King of Great Britain the 9/19 of Decemb. 1673. Copy includes at the end, two texts which read "Extract, Uyt't register der resolutien vande hoogh mogende heeren Staten Generael der Vereenighde Nederlanden. Mercurij den 24 Julij 1658." On A1 of copy 1, catchword: aen; copy 2: de. Reproduction of the original in the Jesus College Library, Oxford.
